# MedVirtual Meta Creative Handoff

Default priority: **graphics-handoff clarity** for the Filipino VA/graphics team — not strategy essays or Meta Ads Manager ops.

## Goal
Keep 15–30 ads in the hopper. Make “do this next” obvious.

## Brand
- Ad-facing: **MedVirtual** only (never MedVirtual.ai)
- Tagline: Staffing Solutions for Every Practice
- Font: Be Vietnam
- Colors: `#077999`, `#00B2E2`, `#0D546B`
- Official SVG logos; MedVirtual-only for Meta ads

## Service model
Hire dedicated full-time virtual staff who join the practice team.
Not a call center / managed front desk / software / “we run your front desk.”

## Visual DNA (one look — Hailey)
Same system for **Role-Offer** (stock roles) and **Real People** (named talent):
light cyan grid plate · Hire a Virtual / Meet {Name} · teal role pill · short checklist · CTA · colored logo · person on light plate.

- Stock Role-Offer: may include approved price stamp / Hire language — `role-offer-templates.html`
- Named Real People: Meet {Name} · exact public role · public skills only · interview CTA — **no invented rates/credentials**

Never dark muddy teal overlays.

## Files
- Public: web-safe handoff assets
- `.local-masters/`: huge video / .ai
- `_private/`: internal docs — never expose to graphics

## Site order
1. Brief  2. Templates (Hailey favorites + Role-Offer)  3. Launch 1 / Launch 2  4. Real People
Reference far right: Brand Guide · Assets · Images

## Workflow
copy form → attach refs (Hailey / Role-Offer + talent photo + logo) → design

No UTM / form QA / campaign shell / audience clutter on graphics pages.

## Claims
Do not invent HIPAA, new rates, savings %, performance, credentials, or availability.
